merchant.name: Omnivore - Oxley @ Raffles
merchant.description:
THE BUZZ: Omnivore is an on the go salad store that offers a pleasant experience with their menu featuring a variety of delicious and nutritious meals. Their concept allows patrons to customise their own salad that consists of the essential nutrients optimal to the food pyramid. Located at Chevron House and just a few minutes away from Raffles Place MRT Station, Omnivore is a great place where families and friends can share and enjoy delectable and healthy dishes in a comfortable and relaxed setting. MUST TRY: Come and try their protein-filled signature Crispy Skin Salmon, Peppered Smoked Duck and Lemongrass Chicken Thigh then pick some carbs like Turmeric Raisin Rice. Then finally, top it all with a variety of toppings like spiced apple, hanjuku egg, Chinese pesto, and more. 
Source: hungrygowhere.com
